descriptionHtml:
Ever wanted to live in a tree house!
Well now you can!
With this custom house you will be to live up in the trees with amazing scenery throughout the location.
Ive picked a perfect place for this home to be located
It contains everything and more you will need for a awesome player home.
type coc treehouse to go to the location
also check the picture for another location
-----
It Contains:
-Smiting Anvil
-Workbench
-Grindstone
-Tanning rack
-Smelting Oven
-Wood Chopin Block
-Alchemy Station
-Arcane Enchanter
-Shrine Of Talos
-Cooking Pot
-Display Cases
-Weapon Racks and Plaques
-Tons of Storage and Extra Storage
-Little Alchemy Garden
